	* ggz-gtk/: about.c, chat.c, chat.h, client.c, ggzclient.c,
	server.c: Fixed a few nasty g_strdup and g_strdup_printf memory
	leaks.
	
	I reviewed all g_strdup_printf calls, and I believe these should
	now all be safe.

